71
00:03:14,417 --> 00:03:16,678
This lets you compare side by side

72
00:03:17,239 --> 00:03:18,840
what is the real impact of the changes.

73
00:03:19,480 --> 00:03:21,121
Are people in the new version?

74
00:03:22,007 --> 00:03:24,548
