00:21:40,381 --> 00:21:42,864
And we created a dashboard for the super KPIs.

503
00:21:43,525 --> 00:21:45,548
It was originally intended for 20 people,

504
00:21:46,069 --> 00:21:47,911
just in the executive team and a bit more.

505
00:21:48,552 --> 00:21:50,615
And it was very widely adopted in the company.

506
00:21:51,556 --> 00:21:53,759
Just to keep in mind, the whole company is about 300 people.

