00:22:35,078 --> 00:22:35,719
Is it actionable?

528
00:22:36,259 --> 00:22:37,039
No, don't do it.

529
00:22:37,860 --> 00:22:39,221
If you know someone is going to use it,

530
00:22:39,301 --> 00:22:40,822
if customer service is going to use it,

531
00:22:40,922 --> 00:22:42,203
if marketing is going to use it,

532
00:22:42,723 --> 00:22:44,544
community managers, yes,

533
00:22:45,185 --> 00:22:47,466
but first validate that it's actionable.

534
00:22:48,171 --> 00:22:51,552
Then ask, does this affect a core KPI 25%?

