00:23:58,484 --> 00:24:00,505
So always make sure that there's something

564
00:24:00,545 --> 00:24:01,326
behind what you're doing.

565
00:24:02,347 --> 00:24:03,287
A lot harder than it sounds.

566
00:24:05,068 --> 00:24:07,710
Okay, let's talk a bit about things that we're doing.

567
00:24:07,870 --> 00:24:08,971
Things that were high impact,

