00:28:09,800 --> 00:28:12,922
they still need to add that record to the action,

678
00:28:13,222 --> 00:28:14,803
but they don't longer depend on anyone else

679
00:28:14,843 --> 00:28:15,603
parsing that for them.

680
00:28:16,650 --> 00:28:18,532
Data engineering became very, very happy

681
00:28:19,313 --> 00:28:20,794
because they were able to do dashboards

682
00:28:21,295 --> 00:28:22,316
like the one I just showed you.

683
00:28:22,736 --> 00:28:24,818
For the executive team, they were able to create

684
00:28:25,479 --> 00:28:27,220
new dashboards for video ads

685
00:28:27,340 --> 00:28:29,022
to help our marketing teams and the games,

686
00:28:29,582 --> 00:28:30,663
and they were working on projects

687
00:28:30,683 --> 00:28:31,905
that had a much higher impact.

688
00:28:34,203 --> 00:28:37,485
One thing to remember, game independence is really good.

689
00:28:37,865 --> 00:28:40,286
And I have, as we speak here,

