00:28:42,707 --> 00:28:44,528
creating tables that I know nothing about.

692
00:28:45,128 --> 00:28:46,249
As the data guy in the company,

693
00:28:46,269 --> 00:28:47,189
I have no idea what they're doing.

694
00:28:47,209 --> 00:28:48,410
They could create anything they want.

695
00:28:48,790 --> 00:28:52,151
They could be doing it for word puzzles, match threes,

696
00:28:52,271 --> 00:28:54,052
they could be creating it for strategy games.

697
00:28:54,732 --> 00:28:55,353
I don't need to know.

