00:29:02,954 --> 00:29:05,455
that's when we have to bring them back into the fold

701
00:29:06,055 --> 00:29:08,556
and make sure that we do everything in an organized manner.

702
00:29:09,036 --> 00:29:10,736
Then I can guarantee they have quality,

703
00:29:11,376 --> 00:29:13,857
that their data is secured, that I'm logging what they're doing,

704
00:29:13,917 --> 00:29:15,277
that I can create things for them.

